match.name: Sundowner RO Match
match.about:
RO's are the leaders of our sport and they get to have their own private match!  Come help with our amazing Sundowner NRL22X match and earn national points while enjoying helping others.

We will provide a pizza dinner for Friday and you will also be served on Saturday with our catered dinner. 

If you would like to be an RO, please contact me directly for a sign-in code.  kent.kingston@deserttech.com or text me at 702-491-4609

Thank you for volunteering, we sincerely appreciate all you do.
